00:19:36.340 --> 00:19:39.510 align:middle line:84%
At the end of the world
where the lions weep,

00:19:39.510 --> 00:19:43.870 align:middle line:84%
here is the place
dreams are born.

00:19:43.870 --> 00:19:46.410 align:middle line:84%
>>Many a Mecha has gone
