00:24:05.309 --> 00:24:06.350 align:middle line:90%
They don't feel any pain.

00:24:06.350 --> 00:24:07.770 align:middle line:84%
We keep their heads
pretty well stocked

00:24:07.770 --> 00:24:09.080 align:middle line:90%
with dopamine and endorphins.

00:24:09.080 --> 00:24:10.620 align:middle line:84%
Plus, we maintain
careful control

00:24:10.620 --> 00:24:13.010 align:middle line:90%
over the serotonin levels.

00:24:13.010 --> 00:24:15.400 align:middle line:84%
Don't want them to drift
off into too deep a sleep.

00:24:15.400 --> 00:24:17.690 align:middle line:84%
They can't be kept
too awake either.

00:24:17.690 --> 00:24:20.413 align:middle line:84%
>>It's better if you don't
think of them as human.

00:24:20.413 --> 00:24:23.299 align:middle line:84%
>>No, they're much
more than that.

00:24:23.299 --> 00:24:26.666 align:middle line:90%


00:24:26.666 --> 00:24:28.600 align:middle line:84%
So hence, it's stolen
most of our miracles.

00:24:28.600 --> 00:24:31.670 align:middle line:90%


00:24:31.670 --> 00:24:33.740 align:middle line:84%
In a way, they
give us hope, hope

00:24:33.740 --> 00:24:35.429 align:middle line:90%
of the existence of the divine.

00:24:35.429 --> 00:24:37.220 align:middle line:84%
I find it interesting
that some people have

00:24:37.220 --> 00:24:39.880 align:middle line:90%
begun to deify the precogs.

00:24:39.880 --> 00:24:41.630 align:middle line:84%
>>Precogs are pattern
recognition filters.

