That's all.

00:24:42.190 --> 00:24:43.730 align:middle line:84%
>>Yet you call
this room a temple.

00:24:43.730 --> 00:24:45.590 align:middle line:90%
>>Just a nickname.

00:24:45.590 --> 00:24:47.760 align:middle line:84%
>>The Oracle is where
