00:24:49.670 --> 00:24:51.650 align:middle line:84%
even if they had to
invent the Oracle.

00:24:51.650 --> 00:24:54.290 align:middle line:84%
>>DYER: So here we have
a near-future dystopia,

00:24:54.290 --> 00:24:57.870 align:middle line:84%
