has actually given lectures
about cities, smart cities

00:26:03.710 --> 00:26:05.900 align:middle line:90%
installing pre-crime.

00:26:05.900 --> 00:26:08.460 align:middle line:84%
And it's done through predictive
algorithms supposedly.

