Sorry.

00:26:23.420 --> 00:26:25.461 align:middle line:84%
>>WEIDNER: No, I think
that's exactly what it is.

00:26:25.461 --> 00:26:29.840 align:middle line:84%
And what I was struck by in
"Minority Report," besides some

00:26:29.840 --> 00:26:33.026 align:middle line:84%
