amount of predictiveness

00:26:33.026 --> 00:26:36.890 align:middle line:84%
that Spielberg has in it, the
things that we are taking for

00:26:36.890 --> 00:26:40.610 align:middle line:84%
granted right now, which
in 2002, were unheard of,

00:26:40.610 --> 00:26:44.190 align:middle line:84%
and yet, they're in the
film all through the film,

00:26:44.190 --> 00:26:47.330 align:middle line:84%
