20 years what you're

00:27:32.420 --> 00:27:33.590 align:middle line:90%
going to see in the future.

00:27:33.590 --> 00:27:36.800 align:middle line:84%
So this was 2002,
and here we are now,

00:27:36.800 --> 00:27:39.560 align:middle line:84%
targeted advertising is
coming into the market.

00:27:39.560 --> 00:27:41.630 align:middle line:84%
It's becoming the norm,
and we're actually

00:27:41.630 --> 00:27:42.710 align:middle line:90%
going to see pre-crime.

00:27:42.710 --> 00:27:44.600 align:middle line:84%
There will be [? smart
? ] cities, pre-crime.

